casebody.data:
MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

91-1712. Horton v. United Ohio Ins. Co.

Guernsey County, No. 90-CA-26. This cause, here on certification of conflict by the Court of Appeals for Guernsey County, was considered in the manner prescribed by law. Upon consideration of the joint application to dismiss,

IT IS ■ ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective April 24, 1992.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
